### Users Service — примеры запросов (IntelliJ HTTP Client / VS Code REST Client)
### Данные как в таблице users на слайде 59 (first_name / last_name отдельно).
@host = http://localhost:8081

### 1. Регистрация Ивана Петрова
# @name signupIvan
POST {{host}}/api/users/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Иван",
  "lastName": "Петров",
  "username": "ivan_petrov",
  "password": "secret123",
  "profileImage": "https://example.com/ivan.png"
}

> {% client.global.set("ivanToken", response.body.authToken);
   client.global.set("ivanId", response.body.userId); %}

### 2. Регистрация Марии Ивановой
# @name signupMaria
POST {{host}}/api/users/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Мария",
  "lastName": "Иванова",
  "username": "maria_ivanova",
  "password": "secret123"
}

> {% client.global.set("mariaId", response.body.userId); %}

### 3. Логин Ивана
POST {{host}}/api/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "ivan_petrov",
  "password": "secret123"
}

### 4. Поиск пользователя по username
GET {{host}}/api/users/search?username=maria_ivanova

### 5. Профиль по id
GET {{host}}/api/users/{{ivanId}}

### --- Внутренние эндпоинты (для других сервисов) ---

### 6. Валидация токена -> userId
POST {{host}}/internal/auth/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "{{ivanToken}}"
}

### 7. Сменить статус на ONLINE (вызывает Messaging Service)
POST {{host}}/internal/users/{{ivanId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "ONLINE"
}

### 8. Batch профилей (для homepage)
POST {{host}}/internal/users/batch
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ids": ["{{ivanId}}", "{{mariaId}}"]
}

### --- Негативные кейсы ---

### 9. Дубль username -> 409
POST {{host}}/api/users/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Иван",
  "lastName": "Клон",
  "username": "ivan_petrov",
  "password": "secret123"
}

### 10. Неверный пароль -> 401
POST {{host}}/api/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "ivan_petrov",
  "password": "wrong"
}
